      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Witness by Moonlight",
        "Client": "Admiral Galleus",
        "Description": "Malzeno has been spotted\r\nin the Citadel. We cannot\r\nmiss this opportunity. Your\r\norders are clear: Go with\r\nFiorayne and defeat Malzeno\r\nonce and for all! ...And do\r\nreturn to us alive.",
